ontributors on Wikipedia.","name":"Noriko Nakagoshi","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"JP","iso_639_1":"ja","name":"日本語","english_name":"Japanese","data":{"biography":"","name":"中越典子","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"","name":"中越典子","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"CZ","iso_639_1":"cs","name":"Český","english_name":"Czech","data":{"biography":"","name":"Noriko Nakagoši","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"HK","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"","name":"中越典子","primary":false}}]}},"person_36801_translations":{"at":1772471558717,"data":{"id":36801,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"Adam Scott (born April 3, 1973) is an American actor, producer, screenwriter, director and podcaster. He is best known for his roles as Ben Wyatt in the NBC comedy Parks and Recreation, Henry Pollard in the Starz comedy series Party Down, Palek in the HBO drama Tell Me You Love Me and Derek Huff in the 2008 film Step Brothers. He has appeared in the Adult Swim comedy Childrens Hospital. He was also on the show NTSF:SD:SUV::, and the annual Adult Swim special The Greatest Event in Television History, which he also created and produced. Scott is the co-host and co-creator of the Earwolf podcast U Talkin' U2 To Me? with Scott Aukerman.","name":"Adam Scott","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"DE","iso_639_1":"de","name":"Deutsch","english_name":"German","data":{"biography":"","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"FR","iso_639_1":"fr","name":"Français","english_name":"French","data":{"biography":"Adam Scott (né le 3 avril 1973) est un acteur, producteur, scénariste, réalisateur et podcasteur américain. Il est surtout connu pour ses rôles de Ben Wyatt dans la comédie Parks and Recreation de NBC, Henry Pollard dans la série comique Party Down de Starz, Palek dans le drame Tell Me You Love Me de HBO et Derek Huff dans le film Frangins malgré eux de 2008. Il est apparu dans la comédie Childrens Hospital. Il a également participé à l'émission NTSF:SD:SUV::, et à l'émission spéciale annuelle d'Adult Swim The Greatest Event in Television History, qu'il a également créée et produite. Scott est le co-animateur et co-créateur du podcast U Talkin' Talking Heads 2 My Talking Head avec Scott Aukerman.","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"IL","iso_639_1":"he","name":"עִבְרִית","english_name":"Hebrew","data":{"biography":"","name":"אדם סקוט","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"KR","iso_639_1":"ko","name":"한국어/조선말","english_name":"Korean","data":{"biography":"","name":"애덤 스콧","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"JP","iso_639_1":"ja","name":"日本語","english_name":"Japanese","data":{"biography":"","name":"アダム・スコット","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"GR","iso_639_1":"el","name":"ελληνικά","english_name":"Greek","data":{"biography":"","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"GE","iso_639_1":"ka","name":"ქართული","english_name":"Georgian","data":{"biography":"","name":"ადამ სკოტი","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"IR","iso_639_1":"fa","name":"فارسی","english_name":"Persian","data":{"biography":"","name":"ادام اسکات","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"MY","iso_639_1":"ms","name":"Bahasa melayu","english_name":"Malay","data":{"biography":"","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"ZA","iso_639_1":"af","name":"Afrikaans","english_name":"Afrikaans","data":{"biography":"","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"UA","iso_639_1":"uk","name":"Український","english_name":"Ukrainian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Адам Скотт","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"RU","iso_639_1":"ru","name":"Pусский","english_name":"Russian","data":{"biography":"💥Адам Пол Скотт. Родился в 1973-ом году в Санта-Крусе, Калифорния, США. Рос в семье с 2-мя старшими братьями. Отец работал преподавателем биологии, а мать была учителем специального образования. Учился в средней школе Харбор в Санта-Крусе. Работает актёром и продюсером. С 2005-го женат на продюсере Наоми Саблан, у пары 2-ое детей: сын Грэм и дочь Франки\n\n🏆Главные награды🏆: номинация на Эмми (2022) [Разделение]\n\n🎬Главные проекты🎬: «Парки и зоны отдыха» (2009), «Разделение» (2022), «Сводные братья» (2008), «Большая маленькая ложь» (2017), «Машина времени в джакузи 2» (2015)\n\n⭐Интересный факт⭐: Адам большой фанат группы R.E.M. и в 2018-ом году вместе с другом начал вести подкаст, посвящённый этой группе","name":"Адам Скотт","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"IN","iso_639_1":"hi","name":"हिन्दी","english_name":"Hindi","data":{"biography":"","name":"एडम स्कॉट","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"SA","iso_639_1":"ar","name":"العربية","english_name":"Arabic","data":{"biography":"آدم بول سكوت (من مواليد 3 أبريل 1973) هو ممثل ومنتج وكوميدي أمريكي. وُلد في سانتا كروز، كاليفورنيا، واشتهر بأدواره في التلفزيون والسينما، حيث يجمع بين الكوميديا والدراما بأسلوب مميز.\n\nأبرز أعماله تشمل دور بين وايت في مسلسل الكوميديا الشهير Parks and Recreation (2009–2015)، حيث نال استحسانًا كبيرًا لدوره كشخصية ذكية وعاطفية. كما حاز على إشادة واسعة في مسلسل الإثارة النفسي Severance (2022–) بدور مارك إس، الذي يتناول موضوع الفصل بين ذكريات العمل والحياة الشخصية.\n\nفي السينما، قدم آدم سكوت أداءً مميزًا في أفلام مثل Step Brothers (2008) بدور ديريك، الأخ الساخر والمزعج، وفيلم The Secret Life of Walter Mitty (2013)، حيث أظهر قدراته في تقديم شخصيات أكثر جدية.\n\nبالإضافة إلى التمثيل، يشارك في تقديم بودكاست كوميدي بعنوان U Talkin’ U2 To Me? مع الكوميدي سكوت أوكرمان. سكوت متزوج من المنتجة ناومي سابلان، ولديهما طفلان.","name":"ادم سكوت","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"TW","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"","name":"亞當·史考特","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"","name":"亚当·斯科特","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"ES","iso_639_1":"es","name":"Español","english_name":"Spanish","data":{"biography":"","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"BR","iso_639_1":"pt","name":"Português","english_name":"Portuguese","data":{"biography":"Adam Scott é um ator norte-americano, mais conhecido por seu papel como Palek no drama da HBO, Tell Me You Love Me. Também foi coadjuvante na comédia de 2008, Step Brother, com Will Ferrell e John C. Reilly. Estreou a série original da Starz, Party Down.","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"BY","iso_639_1":"be","name":"беларуская мова","english_name":"Belarusian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Адам Скот","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"PL","iso_639_1":"pl","name":"Polski","english_name":"Polish","data":{"biography":"Adam Scott (ur. 3 kwietnia 1973) jest amerykańskim aktorem, producentem, scenarzystą, reżyserem i podcasterem. Najbardziej znany jest z ról Bena Wyatta w komedii NBC Parks and Recreation, Henry'ego Pollarda w serialu komediowym Melanż z muchą, Palek w dramacie HBO Powiedz, że mnie kochasz i Dereka Huffa w filmie Bracia przyrodni z 2008 roku. Wystąpił w komedii Adult Swim Childrens Hospital. Wystąpił również w programie NTSF:SD:SUV:: oraz w corocznym programie specjalnym Adult Swim The Greatest Event in Television History, który również stworzył i wyprodukował. Scott jest współprowadzącym i współtwórcą podcastu Earwolf U Talkin' U2 To Me? ze Scottem Aukermanem.","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"MX","iso_639_1":"es","name":"Español","english_name":"Spanish","data":{"biography":"Adam Scott (Santa Cruz, 3 de abril de 1973) es un actor estadounidense. Es conocido por su papel de Henry Pollard en \"Party Down\", Ben Wyatt en \"Parks and Recreation\" y como Mark Scout \"Severance\".\n\nA mediados de la década de los 90, obtuvo sus primeros trabajos profesionales, entre los que se cuentan los largometrajes \"Frankie the Fly\" (1996), en donde actuó junto a Dennis Hopper y Daryl Hannah; \"Ronnie\" (2002), un thriller que lo tuvo como protagonista; \"Toda la verdad\" (2002), protagonizada por Ashley Judd y Morgan Freeman; \"El aviador\" (2004), de Martin Scorsese; o \"The Matador\" (2005), con Pierce Brosnan.\n\nEntre sus últimos trabajos están las películas \"La madre del novio\" (2005), \"The Return\" (2006), \"Lío embarazoso (Knocked Up)\" (2007), \"August\", \"Hermanos por pelotas (Step Brothers)\" (2008) o \"Leap Year\" (2010), y el thriller de horror \"Piranha 3-D\" (2010), Bacherolette (2012), A.C.O.D. (2013), \"La vida secreta de Walter Mitty\" (2013), entre muchas otras.\n\nEn televisión ha participado en las series \"A dos metros bajo tierra\", \"Urgencias (E.R.)\", \"Murder One\", \"NYPD Blue\",\"Party of Five\", \"Wasteland\", \"CSI: Miami\" o \"Ley y orden\", entre otras. También ha interpretado a Palek en la serie \"Tell Me You Love Me\", y a Henry Pollar en \"Party Down\". Entree 2010 y 2015 protagonizó la comedia \"Parks & Recreation\" como el personaje Ben Wyatt.\n\nEn el teatro ha tenido papeles en las producciones \"Uncle Bob\", que se presentó en Los Ángeles, Nueva York y Edimburgo; \"Everett Beekin\" en el South Coast Repertory; \"Romeo y Julieta\" en el Festival de Shakespeare de Berkeley; \"Dealer’s Choice\" y \"Buffalo Hunters\" en el Mark Taper Forum; \"Beirut\" en el Gardner Stage; \"Water and Wine\" en el Met Theatre; y \"Bloody Poetry\" en el Globe Theatre.\n\nAdam Scott vive en Hollywood, California, con su esposa, Naomi Sablan.","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"HK","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"","name":"亞當·史考特","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"MK","iso_639_1":"mk","name":"","english_name":"Macedonian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Адам Скот","primary":false}}]}},"tv_312917_credits":{"at":1772471561339,"data":{"cast":[{"adult":false,"gender":2,"id":1879665,"known_for_department":"Acting","name":"Zhang Yijie","original_name":"Zhang Yijie","popularity":0.7606,"profile_path":"/jRAkmBUxK8Xw9i0eGxRYUtr41Qw.jpg","character":"Shentu Baiqi","credit_id":"697eca8f6608816a1d0e7301","order":0},{"adult":false,"gender":2,"id":3611174,"known_for_de